  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4ce3c952-8d77-4408-8bbb-2697acc11682\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a986aa50-cc14-48d6-8fea-d0475aa7f5ba\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e1c724eb-96ff-4344-9521-a6003334777f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6dd3d026-5273-4715-b39a-d381dba2e684\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1daa9af0-dcce-4050-a1b5-1ff6a9796dcb\">나이가 들어가면서 기억력이 저하되는건 어쩔 수 없겠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4bb7cf3c-a3d1-4b22-92d7-6337fe9617a8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d0888b44-0014-4078-8572-7ad6556ae36e\">노화로 인해 40대 중후반부터 신경세포가 퇴행이 시작된다고 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-64d6b38a-0227-4925-b3b4-d0eee0a89ce6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-739d338e-c643-4973-a48b-adb76db5a509\">(신경세포의 축삭-axon-이 줄어들고, 수초-myelin-가 퇴화된다고 합니다)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-66635f99-a39f-4560-921e-38897872bc04\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1579517a-b576-4e16-96c4-b8b18c31cc41\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4212405a-02d7-4c73-8e97-6d024b93ede7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8889fc48-afea-482d-ac27-b5cd1e1a1407\">기억력 뿐만 아니라 팔다리를 움직이게 해주는 근유을 조절하는 신경세포도 기능이 저하되면서 동작이 느려지거나 운동능력이 저하되죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0bae6a1b-9e78-415c-ae09-569d624e22aa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f9198f03-8228-4bec-860f-2390b6a83b8b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1c6136e1-e82d-4de1-9480-7618e4a746a9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0b36a61c-0225-4b3e-87df-75d3d0accbc0\">노인성 신경계 질환 중 치매는 그 발생 빈도도 높고 발병이후 본인 및 가족, 주변인들의 고통이 크기 때문에 노인분들이 가장 경계하는 질환 중 하나입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cf8b9800-35c7-4ced-a25d-471178aadcd2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7d9fc720-4e5e-41c2-97f1-bf1dac361fd5\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-933795db-a8b1-4dea-818c-08e029efa638\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-00ad78a9-90e2-4196-9e54-fbb3789179a6\">보건소에서 치매검사를 무료로 해주니 주기적으로 검사를 받아보는 것도 도움이 되겠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0a91f46a-5421-4848-8153-fd0a7d15a333\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-455b4fd9-4d4d-41cb-8b84-a6a0a5e59263\">본인이 치매인가 생각하는 분들도 검사를 해보면 치매가 아니거나, &quot;치매 전 단계&quot;라 불리는 &#x27;경도인지장애&#x27; 일 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0ecce27b-ed79-4476-ae6a-975c67a6666e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-81206384-f02e-4365-96ee-64ffb5330d58\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a308e21d-6991-470d-8f3d-5d65de2fa412\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-a308e21d-6991-470d-8f3d-5d65de2fa412\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA5MTFfMjk4/MDAxNjk0NDEyODQ3ODE0.ZT_fUbtQRTWqUiRjysVxcS1hvQCVdTJ7BFX1idPgEtQg.5OZPQWHaa4_AlWdju4fJ03rKL1ajnnjogCP1V124gwQg.JPEG.isuhani/%EC%B9%98%EB%A7%A4.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1080\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1527\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA5MTFfMjk4/MDAxNjk0NDEyODQ3ODE0.ZT_fUbtQRTWqUiRjysVxcS1hvQCVdTJ7BFX1idPgEtQg.5OZPQWHaa4_AlWdju4fJ03rKL1ajnnjogCP1V124gwQg.JPEG.isuhani/%EC%B9%98%EB%A7%A4.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA5MTFfMjk4/MDAxNjk0NDEyODQ3ODE0.ZT_fUbtQRTWqUiRjysVxcS1hvQCVdTJ7BFX1idPgEtQg.5OZPQWHaa4_AlWdju4fJ03rKL1ajnnjogCP1V124gwQg.JPEG.isuhani/%EC%B9%98%EB%A7%A4.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"706\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-db99ea5f-123e-4697-9608-266d92c1015d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3235a854-641b-45bb-9775-95f73d29ddad\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5c5ce997-81f0-4017-b99e-2d54ce8dca3a\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-44f8e76c-1f0c-40e0-903e-2ebdbe287a70\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b9aaa597-0cbf-44cd-bbd5-38349dab9b7b\">근육을 움직여 자극을 줘야 근육이 생기듯이 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b8a0a75a-ea00-461e-87ec-192b4cd8d129\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-feaf05fe-ce76-40f1-a32c-17317d544bc9\">뇌 신경도 자꾸 쓰고 자극을 줘야 건강하게 유지됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-20db4e20-c3d9-4504-ba2f-bda9f9190df2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3998a96a-e94e-48ba-9149-830ef4713ecb\">뭔가를 배우거나, 책이나 신문 등을 읽고 그 내용을 기억하려 노력하는 행위가 도움이 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8a6d2025-ba57-4a23-a527-4ac946c7c94b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b4371927-258a-4c05-baf0-46e6c80c8cc8\">운동도 뇌 신경세포를 건강하게 만들어줍니다. 자신의 근력 및 관절 상태에 맞는 운동을 택해서 꾸준히 운동해주면 좋습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d7060983-00b3-429b-9054-03e8c87797eb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-34b196a2-693e-4634-8030-966dbc55fbda\">독소(Toxin) 즉 안좋은 물질이 몸에 쌓이면 당연히 신체 및 뇌의 기능을 저하시키게 됩니다. 좋은 먹거리, 좋은 식습관을 갖도록 합시다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3b2c8a51-24aa-4eb6-a84e-0b28428a5033\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ce704149-58a1-466c-b1a6-430d8c7b03ab\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f8d53a7e-0c08-408f-b1af-fa76d5fa74c0\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-f8d53a7e-0c08-408f-b1af-fa76d5fa74c0\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA5MTFfMjQ0/MDAxNjk0NDEzOTQ2ODA2.froYlOkjVNzvKptUp1f8cEhV6P2fsfXGf3bUC2XK27Qg.JiLdXfBfJKeyAJJhQbb0j2nQTVsNTTUnj0HlUEe9Ldwg.JPEG.isuhani/%EC%B9%98%EB%A7%A4_%EC%98%88%EB%B0%A9.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1080\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1527\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA5MTFfMjQ0/MDAxNjk0NDEzOTQ2ODA2.froYlOkjVNzvKptUp1f8cEhV6P2fsfXGf3bUC2XK27Qg.JiLdXfBfJKeyAJJhQbb0j2nQTVsNTTUnj0HlUEe9Ldwg.JPEG.isuhani/%EC%B9%98%EB%A7%A4_%EC%98%88%EB%B0%A9.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA5MTFfMjQ0/MDAxNjk0NDEzOTQ2ODA2.froYlOkjVNzvKptUp1f8cEhV6P2fsfXGf3bUC2XK27Qg.JiLdXfBfJKeyAJJhQbb0j2nQTVsNTTUnj0HlUEe9Ldwg.JPEG.isuhani/%EC%B9%98%EB%A7%A4_%EC%98%88%EB%B0%A9.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"706\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8d7ee33d-c2c1-4962-b0e3-fd9b9036528c\">\n              